'''AK031995''' was the identification tag of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] datafiles recovered from ''[[Gnisnal]]''{{'s}} [[Memory bank/Legends|datacore]] and deciphered by [[Ayddar Nylykerka]]. The data contained within AK031995 yielded a breadth of information on the [[Imperial Military/Legends|Imperial]] [[Order of Battle/Legends|order of battle]] and the existence of the [[Black Fleet]].

==Appearances==
*''[[Before the Storm]]''

